et, R., van der Vorst, R., Pearson, P., Leach, M., The European and global potential of carbon dioxide sequestration in tackling climate change (2001) Climate Policy, 1, pp. 155-171; Gruber, N., Keeling, C.D., Bates, N.R., Interannual variability in the North Atlantic carbon sink (2002) Science, 298, pp. 2374-2377; Halmann, M.M., Steinberg, M., (1999) Greenhouse Gas Carbon Dioxide Mitigations Science and Technology, , Lewis Publishers, Washington, DC; Haugan, P.M., Drange, H., Sequestration of CO2 in the deep ocean by shallow injection (1992) Nature, 357, pp. 318-320; Hanisch, C., The pros and cons of carbon dioxide dumping (1998) Environmental Science and Technology, 32 (1), pp. 20A-24A; Herzog, H., Eliasson, B., Kaarstad, O., Capturing greenhouse gases (2000) Scientific American, , Feb. 72-79; Houghton, J.T., Ding, Y., Griggs, D.J., Noguer, M., van der Linden, P.J., Xiaosu, D., (2001) Climate Change 2001: The Scientific Basis, , Cambridge University Press, Cambridge PICC Third Assessment Report: Climate Change 2001; Holloway, S., An overview of the Joule II project ""The underground disposal of carbon dioxide"" (1996) Energy Conversion and Management, 37 (6-8), pp. 1149-1154; (1998) Sleipner Carbon Dioxide Storage Workshop, , 25th-26th November 1997 IEA Trondheim, Norway. Report PH3/1, February 1998. Publ. International Energy Authority Greenhouse Gas R&D Project, Cheltenham, UK; Climate Change and Its Linkages with Development, Equity, and Sustainability (1999) Proceedings of the IPCC Expert Meeting Held in Colombo, , IPCC Sri Lanka, 27-29 April 1999. Edited by Mohan Munasinghe and Rob Swart. ISBN: 90-6960-084-6; Kennett, J.P., Ingram, B.L., A 20,000-year record of ocean circulation and climate change from the Santa Barbara basin (1995) Nature, 377, pp. 510-514; Mana, M.E., Bradley, R.S., Hughes, M.K., Northern hemisphere temperatures during the past millennium: Interferences, uncertainties, and limitations (1999) Geophys. Res. Lett., 26, pp. 759-762; Marchetti, 